  <id>eu.retroshine.RetroShine</id>
  <name>RetroShine</name>
  <summary>Automatic AI-based photo color correction</summary>
  <developer id="eu.retroshine">
    <name>Marius Wanko</name>
  </developer>
  <description>
    <p><em>RetroShine</em> is a free, AI-powered photo color restoration tool designed for batch processing digitized analog images. 
       It automatically adjusts color curves and contrast so “old photos” come alive in one click.</p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Smart auto-correction (curve adjustment by image content)</li>
      <li>Batch processing (entire folders)</li>
      <li>Preserves full resolution and metadata</li>
      <li>Simple interface, no editing experience needed</li>
      <li>Advanced options for precise manual control</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
